00:14:12,920 --> 00:14:13,600
Di Renjie,

256
00:14:15.000 --> 00:14:16.120
keluar dari sini.

257
00:14:23,840 --> 00:14:25,160
Aku ingat kamu berkata

258
00:14:26,200 --> 00:14:27,240
