314
00:16:28,080 --> 00:16:29,560
Orang yang pergi ke tambang

315
00:16:29,560 --> 00:16:30,600
memang bukan kamu

316
00:16:30,920 --> 00:16:31,440
Tetapi

317
00:16:32,080 --> 00:16:33,480
Nona Lai Er,

318
00:16:34,360 --> 00:16:36,360
Adik Yinlian.

319
00:16:36,840 --> 00:16:38,200
Kenapa dia melakukan ini?

320
00:16:39,360 --> 00:16:40,600
Anda harus bertanya padanya,

321
00:16:40,600 --> 00:16:41,720
bukan saya.

322
00:16:41,760 --> 00:16:44,080
Anda tahu persis alasannya.

323
00:16:44,440 --> 00:16:45,440
Nyonya Yinlian

324
00:16:45,440 --> 00:16:46,680
selalu keluar

325
00:16:46,680 --> 00:16:48,800
atas nama kunjungan Nona Lai Er.

326
00:16:48,800 --> 00:16:49,360
Pelayan

327
00:16:49,920 --> 00:16:51,440
dapat bersaksi mengenai hal ini.

328
00:16:52,200 --> 00:16:54,320
Selalu memiliki Tuan Yinlian dan Nona Lai Er
sudah bertemu satu sama lain?

329
00:16:54,840 --> 00:16:55,960
Tidak terlalu.

330
00:16:56,280 --> 00:16:57,280
Saya pernah mendengar mereka dulu mempunyai dendam yang mendalam

331
00:16:57,280 --> 00:16:59,280
melawan satu sama lain.

332
00:16:59,560 --> 00:17:00,840
Itu baru saja terjadi

333
00:17:00,960 --> 00:17:02,080
bahwa mereka mulai bertemu lagi.

334
00:17:02,640 --> 00:17:04,600
Jika Anda tahu mereka berselisih,

335
